                    <span>This book tells it all. From the first chapter on the basics of the internal combustion engine all the way through the details of brake systems and suspensions. Mr. Zimmerman's knowledge of his field is apparent in the way he presents the infornmation on each topic. Illustrations and diagrams are very inforative and easily understood.<br>I'm also giving the book to my 14 year old son so he can get a good base of knowledge to work on his own bikes.<br>Great job!</span>
                  
              
